  <brief_title>Study of Single And Double Bundle Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Graft Cross-sectional Dimensions</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Single And Double Bundle ACL Graft Cross-sectional Dimensions Compared With Native ACL</official_title>
  <sponsors>
